      <h1 class="about-hero-title">Potion Kit</h1>

      <p class="about-hero-description">
        CLI to scaffold and build websites with <a href="https://haroldjs.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Harold</a> and UI Potion: static sites with Handlebars, Markdown, and SCSS only. Chat with the AI to design and build your site; the model uses the UI Potion catalog and Harold conventions and can only suggest components from real specs.
      </p>
